A Typical AI Engineer Workflow

Suppose you receive a machine learning project.

Step 1: Check current location
pwd
Step 2: View files
ls
Step 3: Create project folder
mkdir HousePricePrediction
Step 4: Enter the folder
cd HousePricePrediction
Step 5: Create subfolders
mkdir data models notebooks
Step 6: Create a notes file
cat > README.txt

Type your notes and save.

Step 7: Search for Python files later
find . -name "*.py"
Step 8: Search for a keyword in your code
grep -r "LinearRegression" .

This is very close to what you will do daily in real AI jobs.

